1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
There's a reason your coffee
stops working at 3 PM.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,000
The coffee hits. You feel alert for
20 minutes. Then you're back to dead.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:16,000
By 3 PM, your adenosine buildup is winning. Caffeine blocks adenosine receptors, but they're
overwhelmed. Adding more caffeine just delays the crash — and steals your sleep.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Replace the 3 PM coffee with 10 minutes
of movement. Walk. Stretch. The effect lasts longer.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
I built an app that gives you the
right action at the right time. Free.

